      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·006.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Keih koo..4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>死生契闊，與子成說，執子之手，與子偕老。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>For life or for death, however separated,
To our wives we pledged our word.
We held their hands; —
We were to grow old together with them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-006__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
