      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·006.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Keih koo..5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>于嗟闊兮，不我活兮，于嗟洵兮，不我信兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Alas for our separation!
We have no prospect of life.
Alas for our stipulation!
We cannot make it good.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
